         MACRO
         DATAFILE
TRKHEADR DSECT ,                   TRACK HEADER DEFINITION
TRKCHAIN DS    F                   CHAIN ADDRESS OF NEXT TRACK
TRKDLNTH DS    H                   LENGTH OF DATA HELD ON TRACK
TRKFLAG  DS    X                   TRACK ATTRIBUTE FLAG
TRKCNTL  EQU   X'80'               THIS IS A CONTROL TRACK
TRKDATA  EQU   X'40'               THIS IS A DATA TRACK
TRKFREE  EQU   X'20'               THIS IS A FREE TRACK
TRKFLAG2 DS    X                   UNUSED
TRKHDRLN EQU   *-TRKHEADR          LENGTH OF TRACK HEADER
DATAAREA EQU   *                   START OF DATA AREA OF TRACK
FREEQ    DS    F                   ADDRESS OF FIRST FREE Q TRACK
FILEHDR  EQU   *                   DATAFILE HEADER DEFINTIION
FILENAME DS    CL16                NAME OF THE DATAFILE
FILEADDR DS    F                   TTR OF FIRST TRACK OF DATAFILE
FILELWRI DS    F                   DATA OF LAST WRITE TO FILE
FILELREA DS    F                   DATE OF LAST READ TO FILE
FILERECC DS    F                   NUMBER OF RECORDS ON FILE
FILERLEN DS    H                   LENGTH OF RECORDS ON THE FILE
FILERFRM DS    X                   RECORD FORMAT OF FILE
FILERFIX EQU   X'80'               RECORDS ARE FIXED LENGTH
FILERVAR EQU   X'40'               RECORDS ARE VARIABLE LENGTH
FILEFLAG DS    X                   FILE FLAGS
FILEHLEN EQU   *-FILEHDR           LENGTH OF FILE HEADER
         MEND
